Lock N' Load with R. Lee Ermey (HDTV 720p 2009)  Blades  (01x09)

The history of the various types of blades are examined, with host R. Lee Ermey.  

Gunny explores the history of the weapons that ruled the world for thousands of years before guns came. Featured weapons tests include: Bows and Arrows (English Long Bow vs. Medieval Crossbow), Spears (Roman Pilum) &amp; (Long Pike vs. Lance), Swords (Japanese Katana vs. European Longsword) &amp; (Curved Saber vs. Straight Saber). Gunny gives us a detailed exploration of the tech and design behind swords from ancient Bronze to today's modern day Bayonet, still being used by military around the world.


